Layer	Protocol	Purpose
7 / Application	HTTP, DNS	Actual content of communication
6	TLS	Encrypts the data
4	TCP	Reliable communication (handshake, ACKs)
3	IP	Route across networks (IP addresses)
2	Ethernet	Deliver across local network (MAC addresses)
1 Physical	Frame	Actual bits sent over wire

